getChat(User, User) - Static method in class com.example.solocarry.controller.ChatController
This getChat method gets a chat object from the Firestore "Chat" collection, if first asks user to provide two users, userOne and userTwo, then it combines two users' name as a chat id to query the Firestore, and then the Firestore will return a document reference indicates the document that stored the chat object in cloud database.
